'''凯瑟琳·黛西·科尔曼'''（{{Lang-en|Catherine Daisy Coleman}}，{{bd|1997年|3月30日|2020年|8月4日|catIdx=Coleman}}）是[[美国|美国]][[性虐待|性虐待]]幸存人士支持者、[[女演员|女演员]]和[[制片人|制片人]]。她在14岁时遭受性侵的经历被反映在2016年上映的纪录片《{{Link-en|奥德里与黛西|Audrie & Daisy}}》，而本片也获得了2016年的{{Link-en|电影之眼荣誉奖|Cinema Eye Honors}}。科尔曼与人共同建立了[[非营利组织|非营利组织]]{{lang|en|SafeBAE}}，该组织旨在防止校园性侵案件的发生。黛西·科尔曼于2020年8月4日自杀，得年23岁。

== 早年境况 ==
黛西·科尔曼是梅琳达·科尔曼（Melinda Coleman）与迈克尔·科尔曼（Michael Coleman）的女儿；她的父亲是一名医生，于2009年死于一场交通事故<ref>{{cite web |author1=Patrizia Rizzo |title=What happened to Daisy Coleman’s dad and brother and when did they die? |url=https://www.the-sun.com/news/1267736/daisy-coleman-dad-brother-died-crash-netflix-maryville/ |publisher=[[太陽報_(英國)|美国太阳报]] |accessdate=2020-08-10}}</ref><ref name="Montgomery">{{cite web |author1=Rick Montgomery |title=Daisy Coleman Loses Brother in Truck Crash |url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/56789446/the-kansas-city-star/ |website={{Link-en|家谱网|Ancestry.com|报纸网}} |publisher={{Link-en|堪萨斯城星报|The Kansas City Star}} |accessdate=2020-08-10}}</ref>。她还有三个兄弟。

== 性侵往事 ==
2012年1月，17岁的马修·巴内特（{{lang|en|Matthew Barnett}}）因涉嫌[[强奸|强奸]]和[[性侵|性侵]]当时年仅14岁的黛西·科尔曼而被捕<ref>{{cite web |author1=Joe Kemp |title=Missouri teen writes about allegedly being raped by grandson of politician and target in Maryville community |url=https://www.nydailynews.com/news/national/missouri-teen-writes-raped-grandson-politician-target-maryville-community-article-1.1489769 |publisher=[[纽约每日新闻|纽约每日新闻]] |accessdate=2020-08-10}}</ref>。同时，另一名15岁的男子也因涉嫌强奸和性侵科尔曼的13岁女伴而遭逮捕；此外，另有一名男孩承认用电话记录了巴内特的所谓“侵犯”经过<ref name="Drehle">{{cite web |author1=David Von Drehle |title=A Cold End to Maryville Sexual Assault Case |url=https://time.com/368/a-cold-end-to-maryville-sexual-assault-case/ |publisher=[[时代_(周刊)|时代]] |accessdate=2020-08-10}}</ref><ref name="Caldwell">{{cite web |author1=Maggie Caldwell |title=Anonymous Takes On the Maryville Rape Scandal. Is This a Good Thing? |url=https://www.motherjones.com/crime-justice/2013/10/maryville-anonymous-football-rape-case/ |publisher=[[琼斯母亲|琼斯母亲]] |accessdate=2020-08-10}}</ref>。2013年，该县的检察官撤销了对马修·巴内特的重罪和轻罪指控，因为其是颇具影响力的密苏里州前州众议员{{Link-en|雷克斯·巴内特|Rex Barnett}}的孙子；而同时，[[諾德韋縣_(密蘇里州)|诺德韦县]]检察官却对第三名男孩提起性剥削的重罪指控，这引发了巨大争议<ref name="Drehle" /><ref name="Caldwell" /><ref>{{cite web |author1=Dugan Arnett |title=Nightmare in Maryville: Teens’ sexual encounter ignites a firestorm against family |url=http://www.kansascity.com/2013/10/12/4549775/nightmare-in-maryville-teens-sexual.html |publisher={{Link-en|堪萨斯城星报|The Kansas City Star}} |accessdate=2020-08-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author1=Peggy Lowe |author2=Monica Sandreczki |title=Why Was The Maryville Rape Case Dropped? |url=https://www.kcur.org/community/2013-07-11/why-was-the-maryville-rape-case-dropped |publisher={{Link-en|KCUR调频广播电台|KCUR-FM}} |accessdate=2020-08-10}}</ref>。

2013年10月，有关此案的报道再度喧嚣尘上，这引发了包括[[匿名者|匿名者]]在内诸多网络社区的愤怒<ref>{{cite web |author1=David Von Drehle |title=Hackers Target Town After Dropped Sexual-Assault Case |url=https://nation.time.com/2013/10/14/hackers-target-town-after-dropped-sexual-assault-case/ |publisher=[[时代_(周刊)|时代]] |accessdate=2020-08-10}}</ref>。{{Link-en|迈克尔·沙弗尔 (新闻记者)|Michael Schaffer (journalist)||迈克尔·沙弗尔}}在他为《[[新共和|新共和]]》撰写的有关本案的报道中将案发地{{Link-en|马里维尔 (密苏里州)|Maryville, Missouri|马里维尔}}形容为“不法的人间地狱（{{lang|en|lawless hellhole}}）”<ref>{{cite web |author1=Michael Schaffer |title=Maryville, Missouri Is a Lawless Hellhole |url=https://newrepublic.com/article/115315/maryville-rape-case-maryville-lawless-hellhole |publisher=[[新共和|新共和]] |accessdate=2020-08-10}}</ref>。

2014年，一名{{Link-en|特别检察官|Special prosecutor}}负责重新调查此案。马修·巴内特因涉嫌将儿童带离家庭而危害儿童福利的二级{{Link-en|轻罪|Misdemeanor}}被起诉，最后他被{{Link-en|密苏里州巡回法庭|Missouri Circuit Courts}}法官格伦·迪特里希（{{lang|en|Glen Dietrich}}）判处四个月[[监禁|监禁]]并[[缓刑|缓期]]两年执行的[[感化令|感化令]]<ref name="Drehle" /><ref>{{cite web |author1=Matt Pearce |title=‘The case is closed’: No rape charges in Maryville, Mo., case |url=https://www.latimes.com/nation/nationnow/la-na-nn-maryville-rape-charges-20140109-story.html |publisher=[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]] |accessdate=2020-08-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Maryville, Mo., Sexual Assault Case Comes to an End |url=https://abcnews.go.com/2020/video/maryville-mo-sexual-assault-case-end-21496379 |publisher=[[ABC新闻|ABC新闻]] |accessdate=2020-08-10}}</ref>。而强奸科尔曼的男生则因殴打罪在少年法庭被判刑<ref>{{cite web |author1=Treye Green |title=Who Is Matthew Barnett? 7 Facts To Know About The Accused Maryville Rapist |url=https://www.ibtimes.com/who-matthew-barnett-7-facts-know-about-accused-maryville-rapist-1433070 |publisher=[[国际财经时报|国际财经时报]] |accessdate=2020-08-10}}</ref>。

